                                                                                    <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                                                        <p>Improved app ranking for
                                                                                            keywords like
                                                                                            &#8220;Habit&#8221; and
                                                                                            &#8220;Routine&#8221; in App
                                                                                            Store Japan (top 1), Korea
                                                                                            (top 1) and the United
                                                                                            States (top 10) by A/B
                                                                                            testing keywords in app
