                                                                        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                                            <p>Many One Percents is the first ecosystem
                                                                                of blogs, podcasts, and newsletters
                                                                                about Tech and Productivity in Vietnam.
                                                                                Founded in 2019.</p>
                                                                            <ul>
                                                                                <li>I grew my main blog from <strong>0
                                                                                        to 10,000</strong> visits/month.
                                                                                    North-star metric: Average session
                                                                                    duration &#8211; increased
                                                                                    <strong>20% YoY</strong>.<br />
                                                                                    <em>Achieved #1 ranking on Google
                                                                                        Vietnam for productivity
                                                                                        keywords: Zettelkasten, Habit
                                                                                        trackers, Note taking apps.</em>
                                                                                </li>
                                                                                <li>I grew my newsletter from <strong>0
                                                                                        to ~5,000</strong> subscribers
                                                                                    within less than 2 years</li>
                                                                            </ul>
