                                                                        <div class="wpb_wrapper">
                                                                            <h3><strong>Billboard 100 to Spotify
                                                                                    Playlist</strong></h3>
                                                                            <p>On my best friend’s 24th birthday, I
                                                                                built a small Python program to scrape
                                                                                all the top 100 songs being played the
                                                                                week he was born, and then to create a
                                                                                Spotify playlist of those songs.</p>
                                                                            <p>The program used BeautifulSoup and
                                                                                Spotipy modules.You can check out my
                                                                                program on my Github page <a
                                                                                    href="https://github.com/tuanmonn/PythonProjects/tree/main/pythonCourse/100-days-of-code/day-46-musical-time-machine">over
                                                                                    here</a>.</p>
